<style>
  .luna-rw {
    background: var(--gr-cream-light, #faf8f5);
    padding: 64px 16px;
  }

  .luna-rw__container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .luna-rw__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .luna-rw__header-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .luna-rw__header-stars { display: flex; gap: 2px; }

  .luna-rw__header-count {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a);
  }

  .luna-rw__filter-btn {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.15);
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .luna-rw__filter-btn:hover { background: #fff; }

  .luna-rw__write-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a);
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .luna-rw__write-btn:hover { background: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a); color: #fff; }

  .luna-rw__masonry { columns: 2; gap: 12px; }

  .luna-rw__card {
    break-inside: avoid;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .luna-rw__card-img { aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; position: relative; }

  .luna-rw__card-img img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .luna-rw__card-body { padding: 14px; }

  .luna-rw__card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .luna-rw__card-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a); }
  .luna-rw__card-verified-icon { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .luna-rw__card-verified-text { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gr-green, #3a7d44); font-weight: 500; }
  .luna-rw__card-date { font-size: 10px; color: var(--gr-sage, #7c8c78); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .luna-rw__card-stars { display: flex; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 8px; }

  .luna-rw__card-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .luna-rw__show-more { text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; }

  .luna-rw__show-more-btn {
    padding: 12px 32px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    border: 2px solid var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a);
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .luna-rw__show-more-btn:hover { background: var(--gr-dark, #1a1a1a); color: #fff; }

  .luna-rw__card--hidden { display: none; }

  @media (min-width: 768px) { .luna-rw { padding: 80px 24px; } }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .luna-rw__container { max-width: 1000px; }
    .luna-rw__masonry { columns: 3; }
  }
</style>

<section class="luna-rw" data-section-type="luna-review-wall">
  <div class="luna-rw__container">
    <div class="luna-rw__header">
      <div class="luna-rw__header-left">
        <div class="luna-rw__header-stars">
          {% for i in (1..5) %}
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <span class="luna-rw__header-count">50,000+ Reviews</span>
      </div>
      <button class="luna-rw__filter-btn" aria-label="Filter reviews">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gr-dark)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4" y1="6" x2="20" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/><line x1="11" y1="18" x2="13" y2="18"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <button class="luna-rw__write-btn">Write a review</button>

    <div class="luna-rw__masonry" data-rw-masonry>
      <!-- Review 1 -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card" data-rw-card>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-img"><img src="{{ 'review-mom-toddler.jpg' | prepend: '/images/gruns/' | asset_url }}" alt="Review by Rebecca D." loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Rebecca D.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">6/4/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">We tried every spray and lotion out there. Nothing worked without drenching our kids in chemicals. These patches? Stuck one on each kid before the park &mdash; zero bites. I'm literally never going back to spray. Best purchase I've made all summer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 2 -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card" data-rw-card>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-img"><img src="{{ 'review-patch-arm.jpg' | prepend: '/images/gruns/' | asset_url }}" alt="Review by Jeremy H." loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Jeremy H.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">6/3/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">I used to buy those coil things, candles, sprays &mdash; spending $40+ a month in summer. One pack of these lasts the whole season for less than $15. It's a no-brainer. My wife ordered 3 more packs for the grandparents.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 3 (no image) -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card" data-rw-card>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Sarah M.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">6/1/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">My toddler thinks they're dinosaur stickers and wants to put them on himself every morning. Meanwhile, he hasn't had a single mosquito bite in 3 weeks. Parent win. The fun designs are such a smart touch!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 4 -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card" data-rw-card>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-img"><img src="{{ 'review-woman-box.jpg' | prepend: '/images/gruns/' | asset_url }}" alt="Review by Amanda K." loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Amanda K.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">5/29/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">As someone with eczema, I can't use DEET products. These patches don't touch my skin directly and the citronella oil actually keeps bugs away. Game changer for sensitive skin families.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 5 (no image) -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card" data-rw-card>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Marcus T.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">5/27/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">Peel, stick, done. No greasy hands, no reapplying every hour, no chasing my kids around with a spray bottle. Threw a pack in the diaper bag and forgot about it. That's the dream. 10/10 would recommend.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 6 -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card" data-rw-card>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-img"><img src="{{ 'review-hikers.jpg' | prepend: '/images/gruns/' | asset_url }}" alt="Review by Lisa R." loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Lisa R.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">5/25/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">Took these on a 4-day camping trip with the family. We used maybe 20 patches total for 4 people. Not a single bite the entire trip. The kids actually wanted to wear them because of the fun designs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 7 (hidden) -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card luna-rw__card--hidden" data-rw-card data-rw-hidden>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">David P.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">5/22/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">Living in Florida, mosquitoes are a year-round problem. These patches have been an absolute lifesaver. I keep a pack in the car, one at home, and one at the office. The subscription means I never run out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 8 (hidden) -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card luna-rw__card--hidden" data-rw-card data-rw-hidden>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-img"><img src="{{ 'review-woman-selfie.jpg' | prepend: '/images/gruns/' | asset_url }}" alt="Review by Nicole W." loading="lazy" /></div>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Nicole W.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">5/20/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..4) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">Really impressed with how well these work. My only note is I wish the adhesive was slightly stronger &mdash; one fell off during a really sweaty hike. But for everyday use, parks, backyard hangouts? Perfect.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 9 (hidden) -->
      <div class="luna-rw__card luna-rw__card--hidden" data-rw-card data-rw-hidden>
        <div class="luna-rw__card-body">
          <div class="luna-rw__card-meta">
            <span class="luna-rw__card-name">Chris B.</span>
            <svg class="luna-rw__card-verified-icon" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gr-green)"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg>
            <span class="luna-rw__card-verified-text">Verified</span>
          </div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-date">5/18/2026</p>
          <div class="luna-rw__card-stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="var(--gr-accent)"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84 5.34.78-3.87 3.77.91 5.32L10 13.27l-4.77 2.51.91-5.32L2.27 6.69l5.34-.78L10 1z"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
          <p class="luna-rw__card-text">Bought these for a destination wedding in Costa Rica. Every guest got a pack in their welcome bag. Zero complaints, zero bites, and everyone asked where to buy them. Best wedding favor decision ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="luna-rw__show-more" data-rw-show-more>
      <button class="luna-rw__show-more-btn" data-rw-show-more-btn>Show All Reviews</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function() {
  var section = document.querySelector('[data-section-type="luna-review-wall"]');
  if (!section) return;
  var btn = section.querySelector('[data-rw-show-more-btn]');
  var container = section.querySelector('[data-rw-show-more]');
  if (!btn) return;
  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
    section.querySelectorAll('[data-rw-hidden]').forEach(function(card) {
      card.classList.remove('luna-rw__card--hidden');
    });
    container.style.display = 'none';
  });
})();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Luna Review Wall",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "luna-review-wall-section",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
